name: Corporal Vandolay (V)
Lore: 'ISB attache to the Executor. Detention Officer. Political Liaison for COMPNOR. Responsible for all prisoner transfers. Fiercely loyal to the Emperor''s New Order.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Opponent''s smugglers are forfeit -2. During any control phase, may take one Spice Mines Of Kessel into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Once per game, may take an Immediate Effect and/or a prison into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
